imdb.plot outline: Plus 234 is a distinctive drama series brought to you by Rushing Tap. It tells the story of the average working class Nigerian; being in an environment with the same people for a minimum of 8 hours a day, 5 days a week, every week and every year. This naturally creates bonds, conflicts and drama. It breeds love, betrayal, office politics and laughter - all of which is captured in this brand new series you would not want to miss.
